::Slayer::

Slayer replies, also switching frequencies. "Allright. I'll see about 
this bot."

He swoops down, calling out a "Hello?" to anyone that would be in the 
forest under him. He was still a long way from the Maximal base, so 
he had no worries about anyone but this new bot hearing him.
